commentable_entity.title: Kevin smith: Johnny Depp for joker
commentable_entity.description: How amazing would it be to watch Johnny depp play joker! Johnny Depp is one of the best actors of our generation and the best character actor of all time. I think he would do an amazing job! Amber heard has attempted to ruin his life and career, we can’t give her that satisfaction. I would be devastated if he was black listed because of Ambers false accusations. Imagine him in character as the joker, that would be priceless! Imagine his creative take on joker and all the humor he would bring to his character..  I don’t know about you, and I can only speak for myself but Johnny Depp has never let me down, I have throughly enjoyed every single movie I have seen him in . His creativity and attention to detail is mind blowing, he is unpredictable and mysterious which is why you never know what to expect when your watching one of his films. He always gives it his best and makes the character he is portraying his own. Please sign this petition in the hopes that he will be chosen for our next Joker! Thank you all for your time !

commentable_entity.title: Kevin smith: Johnny Depp for joker
commentable_entity.description: How amazing would it be to watch Johnny depp play joker! Johnny Depp is one of the best actors of our generation and the best character actor of all time. I think he would do an amazing job! Amber heard has attempted to ruin his life and career, we can’t give her that satisfaction. I would be devastated if he was black listed because of Ambers false accusations. Imagine him in character as the joker, that would be priceless! Imagine his creative take on joker and all the humor he would bring to his character..  I don’t know about you, and I can only speak for myself but Johnny Depp has never let me down, I have throughly enjoyed every single movie I have seen him in . His creativity and attention to detail is mind blowing, he is unpredictable and mysterious which is why you never know what to expect when your watching one of his films. He always gives it his best and makes the character he is portraying his own. Please sign this petition in the hopes that he will be chosen for our next Joker! Thank you all for your time !

comment:
I am signing this petition because Johnny Depp is one of my personal hero’s. He is such a humble, caring and beautiful human being and it sickens me that Amber heard took advantage of that for her own personal gain.  She truly underestimated his fans and all the people who love him. She accused him of all these outrageous accusations to ruin him but the truth has come out and she is actually the abuser. She disgusts me.. The movie industry would NOT be the same without him. Producers and writers need to know that we the people still stand by him and love him! I genuinely would love to see him play joker, with his own twist’s and humor. 
#JusticeforJohnny
